msgid "Sieve - Faceted Filter for WooCommerce"
msgstr "Sieve – Facettenfilter für WooCommerce"

msgid "https://plogins.com/sieve/"
msgstr "https://plogins.com/sieve/"

msgid "Fast, accessible faceted filtering for WooCommerce and WordPress. Beautiful facet widgets, AJAX filtering with no page reload, a mobile filter drawer, and Core Web Vitals by design."
msgstr "Schnelle, zugängliche Facettenfilterung für WooCommerce und WordPress. Wunderschöne Facetten-Widgets, AJAX-Filterung ohne Neuladen der Seite, eine mobile Filterschublade und Core Web Vitals by Design."

